<plot>After the death of Joanna Dresari during the freeing of Kentaris IV, Ian Dresari has taken the Ducal Throne, but not all is peaceful, as two of his allies refuse to associate with his heavy-handed tactics. House Steiner hires the Black Knight Legion to attempt another assault upon the planet in the guise of freeing it from Duke Ian's oppressive regime. But when trapped between Dresari's forces and the Lyran Military, The Legion has to fight through both sides to survive.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?363162</url></doc>
